@startuml
title Composable attack: from bridge forgery to bad debt
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor #FDF6E3
  BorderColor #657B83
  FontColor #073642
}
start
:Attacker forges the cross-chain\nmessage the bridge relies on;
:Bridge wrongfully attests that\nremote collateral exists and is real;
:Mint an unbacked amount of the\nasset on the destination chain\n(fake supply);
:Deposit the unbacked asset as\ncollateral in a lending vault that\nalready whitelisted it;
:Borrow real assets against the\nunbacked collateral;
:Attacker exits with the real assets;
:Lending protocol is left with\nbad debt;
stop
@enduml
